{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"alias":"spiny-micro-ladle","description":"# S5 — Gerrit -> GitHub one-way replication (core plugin, non-force, deploy key)\n\n## Why\nMake Gerrit the sole writer of GitHub `main`. The core, Apache-2.0, WAR-bundled\n`replication` plugin (push) is the right tool — the GerritForge BSL re-license (2025-09-30)\ntouched only `pull-replication` / multi-site, not this plugin.\n\n## What\n- `replication.config`:\n  - `push = refs/heads/main:refs/heads/main` + `push = refs/tags/*:refs/tags/*`\n    (NON-force — no leading `+`).\n  - `mirror=false` (true does a destructive prune of remote refs absent/invisible locally).\n  - `replicatePermissions=false` (don't leak `refs/meta/config`); explicit refspecs so\n    `refs/changes/*` is never pushed.\n  - finite `replicationMaxRetries`; a `timeout`.\n- Identity: a write-enabled, passphrase-less GitHub deploy key on the rebar repo; the\n  private key sourced from SSM; `~/.ssh/config` IdentityFile + seeded `known_hosts`.\n\n## Scope\nIn: replication plugin config + the deploy-key identity + push of `main` + tags. Out: the\nGitHub-side lockdown that makes the mirror read-only (S6).\n\n## Files\n- `infra/gerrit/replication.config`, deploy-key provisioning under `infra/` + SSM\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- [ ] A change submitted in Gerrit replicates `main` to the GitHub repo (non-force,\n      fast-forward); tags replicate.\n- [ ] `refs/changes/*` and `refs/meta/config` are NOT pushed to GitHub (explicit refspecs +\n      `replicatePermissions=false`).\n- [ ] `mirror=false` (no destructive remote pruning); `replication_log` shows clean,\n      bounded-retry pushes.\n- [ ] The replication identity is a single-repo write deploy key whose private key is sourced\n      from SSM (no plaintext key committed to VCS).","id":"4e82-6034-6d5a-4d39","parent_id":"d251-05e1-eb55-43b2","priority":2,"tags":["gerrit","github","replication"],"ticket_type":"story","title":"infra: S5 — Gerrit->GitHub one-way replication (core plugin, non-force, deploy key)"},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1782685506045700001,"uuid":"a70122c8-8c42-4ea9-8edf-42823077e0e8"}